                                      ↓                                          ↓
                                              [both done]
                                                    ↓
                              ┌─ 7. FE ║ 8. BE ║ 13. Data ║ 14. DevOps ─┐ (paralel, scope'a göre skip)
                              ↓                                           ↓
                                              [all done/skipped]
                                                    ↓
                                              15. Code Reviewer
                                                    ↓
                                              9. Integrator
                                                    ↓
                       ┌── 10. QA ║ 16. Security ║ 17. A11y ║ 18. Perf ──┐ (paralel, scope'a göre skip)
                       ↓                                                  ↓
                                              [all green]
                                                    ↓
                                              11. Promoter (test→main)
                                                    ↓
                                              19. Release Manager
                                                    ↓
                                              20. Observer (30dk canary)
                                                    ↓
                                              21. Retrospective (24h sonra)
                                                    ↓
                                                   DONE ─────► 23. Knowledge Curator (haftalık, retro'dan besleniyor)

[CROSS-CUTTING]
